.Dd 2021-01-26
.Dt REBOOT 8
.Os init #VERSION#
.Sh NAME
.Nm reboot
.Nd reboot the system
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
is a wrapper script to send
.Dq INT
signal to
.Xr init 8
and initiate the shutdown sequence by executing
.Dq /etc/rc.shutdown reboot .
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr poweroff 8 ,
.Xr init 8 ,
.Xr halt 8 .
